WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.780 --> 00:00:07.690
It's extremely hot this afternoon and there
is only one way to beat the heat.

00:00:07.690 --> 00:00:14.150
I'd say it is about Cendol time.

00:00:14.150 --> 00:00:16.920
Must have Cendol!

00:00:16.920 --> 00:00:20.620
It is Cendol time!

00:00:20.620 --> 00:00:22.460
Thank you!

00:00:22.460 --> 00:00:30.390
Here we have our delicious treat.

00:00:30.390 --> 00:00:45.999
We are having Cendol right now and it is a
dessert that is really popular in SE Asia.

00:00:45.999 --> 00:00:46.999
It is made using shaved ice, palm sugar and
it has coconut milk along with little green

00:00:46.999 --> 00:00:50.920
worm-like creatures that are actually made
using rice and beans.

00:00:50.920 --> 00:00:53.880
That is it.

00:00:53.880 --> 00:01:08.610
I honestly couldn't think of a more refreshing
treat or dessert to beat this heat and humidity.

00:01:08.610 --> 00:01:10.000
It is just brilliant.

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:11.792
What do you have there on that spoon?

00:01:11.792 --> 00:01:12.792
I've got some beans!

00:01:12.792 --> 00:01:13.792
Beans?

00:01:13.792 --> 00:01:14.792
Beans for dessert?

00:01:14.792 --> 00:01:15.792
That's a first.

00:01:15.792 --> 00:01:18.700
The green jellies here are actually made out
of rice flour and they have sort of a worm

00:01:18.700 --> 00:01:20.880
like consistency.

00:01:20.880 --> 00:01:23.060
Green worms!

00:01:23.060 --> 00:01:26.329
No, they're fine.

00:01:26.329 --> 00:01:28.509
They're good.

00:01:28.509 --> 00:01:48.740
I'm a happy satisfied and most importantly
refreshed customer.

00:01:48.740 --> 00:02:19.580
This special one that we're getting outside
has a scoop of ice cream in it.

00:02:19.580 --> 00:02:29.140
It's even more delicious.

00:02:29.140 --> 00:02:36.621
Okay, what is this little treat?

00:02:36.621 --> 00:02:59.161
This little tasty treat here that comes in
a bag and is five pieces.

00:02:59.161 --> 00:03:00.161
It is fried banana which was two Ringgit which
is like sixty cents.

00:03:00.161 --> 00:03:01.161
So yummy?

00:03:01.161 --> 00:03:01.171
It is just as good indoors as it is outdoors.

